title: Haitian Medical Facilities
name: Haitian Medical Facilities
description:
This spreadsheet is the product of having 5 different hospital datasets
(from various agencies) with most having different coordinates or naming
convention.  This is my best attempt at cleaning up those datasets into
one document.  
About the data:  PAHO has released a spreadsheet with address,
operational status (# beds), and contact information which was
incorporated into this release.  Damage reports are updated by PAHO or
attributed by individual products found on APAN.  The assessments are
not conclusive at this time.  If I had a choice on the facility name
(spelling), I incorporated PAHO's description since they are conducting
most of the site visits.  This will allow for easier updating in the
future.  The last PAHO report is January 25, 2010. 

Please list PDC, PAHO, Sahana, OSM, OFDA, MINUSTAH, and NAVTEQ as
contributors.   
Any questions can be e-mailed to jlivengood@pdc.org.  We have other
datasets that are being served up as WMS/WFS/AGS feeds.  Unfortunately
we don't have KML at this time.  If you would like to see our other
datasets, please visit http://www.pdc.org/atlas
